The date the first version of the preprint was posted, according to the preprint server.
The date the journal that published the article received a first submission, according to the metadata provided by the publisher.
The date the journal published the article, according to the metadata provided by the publisher.
Number of days between date_journal_submission and date_preprint. Positive values indicate that the preprint was deposited before submission to the journal.
Number of days between date_publication and date_preprint. Positive values indicate that the preprint was deposited before publication.
